<plot>Amigo tries to preserve his moral firmnes and his lifestyle in spite of the unstable social circumstances in Slovenia, a country in transition. The price he is forced to pay for his moral stand is very high. He hits a wall head-on: symbolically and literally. Just as the French medieval poet Francois Villon, he appears to be serving both, God and the Devil.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?035463</url></doc>
